## Local Usage

### Keep These Files Locally
- `hiremitra-skill/` - For reference when building platforms
- `REBRANDING_GUIDE.md` - For renaming your platform
- `TESTING_GUIDE.md` - For manual testing
- `UI_IMPROVEMENTS.md` - For UI documentation

### Access When Needed
```bash
# On your machine (not in GitHub)
cat REBRANDING_GUIDE.md
cat TESTING_GUIDE.md
```

